(In reply to comment #0)
> This is with the current (as of a few minutes ago) development version
> of Batik, on windows XP and jdk 1.5.0_06.

I was unable to reproduce this using JDK 1.6.0_12 on Windows XP SP3 for the current development version (revision 755843): CPU usage keeps low and memory usage is steady. I've made a set of different combination of mouse over:
 * Mouse over between FOO and BAR;
 * Mouse over between FOO/BAR and the document canvas;
 * Mouse over between FOO, BAR and the document canvas (in circles);

I'm tentatively marking this fixed (works for me), as commits and related bug fixes are unknown. Please reopen or add more information if this doesn't feel right. ;-)
